
// This Hyperlambda code snippet replaces all occurrences of the period character "." in the value of the [type] node with an underscore "_". It uses the [strings.replace] slot to perform the replacement operation and then assigns the modified string back to the [type] node using the [set-value] slot.
set-value:x:@.type
   strings.replace:x:@.type
      .:.
      .:_
